      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-repair-500/50 pl-4 text-left">
        ts-repair collapses the compile&ndash;fix iteration loop by using the TypeScript compiler as a verification oracle, producing verified fixes up front instead of heuristic guesses.
      </p>

      <div class="code-block inline-block mb-8 text-left">
        <pre><code><span class="text-gray-500">$</span> npm install -g ts-repair</code></pre>
      </div>

