    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">What ts-repair Fixes (and What It Doesn't)</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        ts-repair is optimized for high-fan-out root-cause errors that generate large diagnostic cascades.
      </p>

